<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hesap360 | Finansal Karşılaştırma Merkezi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #020617; --surface: #0f172a; --primary: #3b82f6; --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); --text-dim: #94a3b8; }
        body { background: var(--bg); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #fff; margin: 0; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -10%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%); min-height: 100vh; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
        nav { padding: 30px 0; text-align: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }
        .hero { padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.8rem); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .hero h1 span { color: var(--primary); }
        .hero p { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 1.15rem; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; }
        .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .service-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px 30px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: 0.3s; }
        .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
        .service-card i { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 24px; display: block; }
        footer { margin-top: 80px; padding: 40px 0; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .footer-links { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .footer-links a { color: var(--text-dim); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; }
        .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <nav><a href="/" class="logo">HESAP<span>360</span></a></nav>
    <header class="hero">
        <h1>Finansal Kararınızı<br><span>Şansa Bırakmayın.</span></h1>
        <p>En uygun kredi ve en yüksek mevduat getirisi ile tasarruf etmeye bugün başlayın.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="services-grid">
        <a href="/kredi" class="service-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-dollar"></i><h3>Kredi Karşılaştır</h3><p>En düşük faizli kredileri listeleyin.</p></a>
        <a href="/mevduat" class="service-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-piggy-bank"></i><h3>Mevduat Getirisi</h3><p>Birikimlerinize en yüksek getiriyi bulun.</p></a>
        <a href="/kredi-limit" class="service-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i><h3>Limit Analizi</h3><p>Kredi çekme potansiyelinizi öğrenin.</p></a>
        <a href="/kredi-karti" class="service-card"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i><h3>Kredi Kartları</h3><p>Kart avantajlarını inceleyin.</p></a>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="/bilgi/hakkimizda">Hakkımızda</a>
            <a href="/bilgi/kosullar">Kullanım Koşulları</a>
            <a href="/bilgi/kvkk">KVKK</a>
            <a href="/bilgi/iletisim">İletişim</a>
        </div>
        <p>© 2026 Hesap360. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</p>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
